{"type": "article", "id": 29638, "title": "极简挂镜", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-14T23:02:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160714230900Mzhf8tmFgV9q0YLk.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>镜子作为一款日常家居用品似乎很少与使用者之间进行互动，来自法国的 <a href=\"http://www.studiobrichetziegler.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Studio Brichet Ziegler</a> 希望通过这面名为 Nello 的镜子改变人们对这一物件的刻板印象，让它作为一种室内装饰与光线产生互动。镜面被安装在两面打磨过的金属片外，中间夹有橡皮绳和上漆的木质组件。尽管如此，镜子从侧面看并没有带给人厚重的感觉，可以很自然地融入周围的环境当中。Nello 一共有三个尺寸，直径分别为 30、55 和 80 厘米。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714231011LB5l6xdqS1ANIoJr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714231011SH1UXfEOK5sFWgMb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714231012y8iDo2vL0trjZ5VN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607142310129VexvcI0NTk6YRWF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}